Asset                   Create a new Asset.
Container               Create a new Asset.
StandardProperties      Create a new 'StandardProperties' list.
active_user             Gets the active user id or 'NULL'.
add_asset               Adds an Asset to the Thot project. The
                        associated data should be saved at the return
                        path.
asset_from_json         Converts a list of properties to an Asset. The
                        list should mirror the structure of the JSON
                        representation of an Asset.
container_by_path       Gets a Thot Container from its path.
container_from_json     Converts a list of properties to a Container.
                        The list should mirror the structure of the
                        JSON representation of a Container.
container_path          Gets a Thot Container's path.
database                Create a new Thot database connection.
database_available      Checks if a Thot database is available.
database_server_path    Get the path to the correct database server.
escape_str              Escape special string characters. Characters
                        escaped: * Backslash (\)
find_asset              Finds a single Asset matching the given filter
                        criteria. If multiple matching Assets are
                        found, a random one is returned.
find_assets             Find Assets matching the given filter criteria.
find_container          Finds a single Container matching the given
                        filter criteria. If multiple matching
                        Containers are found, a random one is returned.
find_containers         Find Containers matching the given filter
                        criteria.
get_container           Gets a Thot Container.
join_path_windows       Normalize Windows paths. If total path length
                        is less than 256, returns the normalized path,
                        otherwise returns the device (UNC) path.
json_asset              Creates a new core Asset.
json_empty_list_to_obj
                        Converts an empty object ([]) in JSON to an
                        empty object ('{}')
load_graph              Loads a Thot Project's graph.
load_project            Loads a Thot project.
project_resource_root_path
                        Gets the Project path given a path. Returns
                        'NULL' if the path is not in a project.
root                    Gets the root Container of the database.
send_cmd                Send a command to the database.
thot_container_id       Gets the 'THOT_CONTAINER_ID' environment
                        variable.
to_json                 Convert an object into JSON.
utc_now                 Datetime in ISO 8601 format.
zmq_socket              Create a ZMQ socket.
